IMAPAccount accelya
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
Host outlook.office365.com
SSLType STARTTLS
User antonio.ruiz@accelya.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/.password-store/mbsync/accelya.gpg"
Timeout 120
PipelineDepth 50

IMAPStore accelya-remote
Account accelya

MaildirStore accelya-local
Inbox ~/.mail/Accelya/Inbox
Path ~/.mail/Accelya/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel accelya
CopyArrivalDate yes
Create Both
Expunge Both
Far :accelya-remote:
Patterns INBOX "Sent Items" Drafts Archive Trash
Remove None
Near :accelya-local:
SyncState *

